JOHANNESBURG - EFC 68 takes place in Cape Town on the 31 March with a tantalising main card of pure combat action. The Clinch spoke to EFC fighters and crew backstage at EFC 67 to get their main card predictions. In this penultimate episode, we get their picks for the lightweight co-main event between Dave 'Pain Train' Mazany (15-6) and Chris Bright (6-0) eNCA